title: Pixel 4 takes blurry pictures compared to same picture taken with a Pixel 3a
content:
My Pixel 4 is taking blurry pictures that are not actually detailed or sharp compared to the same picture taken with my wife's Pixel 3a under the same circumstances, Pixel 4 pictures look so bad quality that looks like they were taken with a cheap phone :(.
